{"title":"梦见字打架","authors":["剑鸣"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":2,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦见字打架"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剑鸣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨夜的梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说来可怕："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦见我写的大楷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在抽屉里打架，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打得墨水乱溅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"溅污了我的鼻子、嘴巴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清早在镜子前一瞧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"事情可更糟糕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦见的全是事实，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我脸上真有墨迹一道道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抽屉里那张大楷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歪的歪来倒的倒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“大”字打拆一条腿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“羊”字撞断一只角，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“鸡”字掉进沟里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难看呀，湿漉漉一身毛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这张字怎能交给老师看呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我急得大吵大闹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸走来瞧一瞧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他望着我好笑："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“就凭你脸上的墨迹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也看得出你写字的‘功劳’，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不相信字会打架，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但我知道："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漂亮整齐的中国字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不会服从粗心孩子的领导。”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}